&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case Development:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Initiate contacts with potential clients. Work with the Director to determine next action in respect of legal matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leading significant matters:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Take the primary leading role in advancing our strategy before international courts and appellate courts nationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal strategy:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Devise legal strategies that will advance our objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
